# Pilates Platform

A SaaS MVP for Pilates instructors вЂ” centralizes scheduling, class plans (templates + per-instance), exercise library with progressions, client roster/attendance, and session notes.

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | Next.js 16 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript 5 |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 (PostCSS), shadcn UI (base-nova style) |
| State | React Context (`AuthProvider`), no external state library |
| API Client | Custom `fetch` wrapper (`src/lib/api.ts`) with `credentials: "include"` |
| Backend | Express 4, TypeScript 5, `express-async-errors` |
| Database | PostgreSQL + Prisma 7 ORM |
| Auth | Better Auth (cookie-based sessions, email/password, Prisma adapter) |
| Validation | Zod 4 (server-side request validation) |
| Uploads | Cloudinary + multer (exercise images) |
| Monorepo | Root `package.json` with `concurrently` |

