## Development Commands

```bash
# Root (runs both client and server concurrently)
npm run dev

# Client only
npm run dev --prefix client        # next dev
npm run build --prefix client      # next build
npm run lint --prefix client       # eslint

# Server only
npm run dev --prefix server        # tsx watch src/index.ts
npm run build --prefix server      # tsc
npm run start --prefix server      # node dist/index.js
```

## Key Conventions

### General
- **TypeScript everywhere**: all code (client and server) must be written in TypeScript with strict mode enabled вЂ” no plain `.js` files, no `any` unless absolutely unavoidable
- **Documentation lookup**: always use the **Context7 MCP** (`resolve-library-id` в†’ `get-library-docs`) to fetch up-to-date documentation before using or advising on any library, framework, or tool вЂ” even well-known ones (Next.js, React, Prisma, Tailwind, Express, Zod, etc.)

### Backend
- **Modular structure**: each feature lives in `server/src/modules/<feature>/` with `routes`, `service`, and `validation` files
- **Validation**: Zod schemas validate request bodies via `validate()` middleware
- **Error handling**: throw `AppError` subclasses (`ConflictError`, `UnauthorizedError`) вЂ” caught by global `errorHandler`; ZodError в†’ 400 with `details`
- **Auth**: Better Auth handles `/api/auth/*` via `toNodeHandler`; protected routes use `authenticate` middleware which reads the session cookie via `auth.api.getSession()`; `req.user` is `{ instructorId, email }`; routes mount at `/api/<module>`
- **Prisma**: client imported from `src/lib/prisma.ts`; generated output at `src/generated/prisma`
- **Soft deletes**: `deletedAt` field on applicable models

### Frontend
- **"use client"** directive on interactive pages and layout components
- **Auth gate**: `AppLayout` redirects unauthenticated users to `/login`; `AuthProvider` wraps Better Auth's `useSession()` hook
- **Auth client**: `authClient` from `@/lib/auth-client` вЂ” provides `signIn.email()`, `signUp.email()`, `signOut()`, `useSession()`
- **Path alias**: `@/*` maps to `./src/*`
- **Component organization**: layout shell in `components/layout/`, shadcn primitives in `components/ui/`
- **API calls**: use the `api` helper from `@/lib/api` вЂ” sends `credentials: "include"` for cookie-based auth; resolves the base URL from `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`

### Database Models (Prisma)
- `Instructor` вЂ” identity & auth (mapped as Better Auth's `user` via `user.modelName`)
- `Session`, `Account`, `Verification` вЂ” Better Auth managed tables
- `ExerciseFolder`, `Exercise`, `ExerciseImage` вЂ” exercise library with progressions
- `ClassPlanTemplate`, `PlanSection`, `PlanSectionExercise` вЂ” class plan templates
- `Class`, `ClassInstance` вЂ” scheduling (GROUP/PRIVATE, recurrence)
- `Client`, `Enrollment`, `Attendance` вЂ” client roster
- `SessionNote`, `SessionNoteExercise` вЂ” per-instance notes
